OL,3,CWhat do you do if you don't have ID to
OL,4,Cvote in the General Election?
OL,6,FThe UK General Election on 4 July is
OL,7,Ffast approaching and for the first
OL,8,Ftime voters will require ID when going
OL,9,Fto the polls.
OL,11,FBut what happens if you haven't got ID?
OL,13,FYou need to act quick.
OL,15,FYou can apply for a free voter ID
OL,16,Fdocument, which is called a Voter
OL,17,FAuthority Certificate but the deadline
OL,18,Fto apply for this is 5pm on Wednesday
OL,19,F26 June.
