OL,3,CWhat do you do if you don't have ID to
OL,4,Cvote in the General Election?
OL,6,FNirushan Sudarsan from the forum says
OL,7,Fhe doesn't want anyone to miss out on
OL,8,Fusing their vote.
OL,10,F"Part of our work is making sure
OL,11,Fpeople from diverse backgrounds from
OL,12,Flots of parts of the world who have
OL,13,Fsettled in Grangetown, can talk to
OL,14,Ftheir friends, they can talk to their
OL,15,Ffamilies to understand actually that
OL,16,Fyou do need voter ID regardless of
OL,17,Fyour age.
